originalText.text: Poor customer service follow up with their scholars edge. submitted paperwork to make an account transfer and failed but didn’t get any sort of notice that it failed. Months passed by. Resubmitted paperwork and more time passed by without confirmation. Followed up to see if the transfer went through and it did but was missing information on the fund allocation. If I didn’t follow up the money would have sat there for years without any returns. 1 star for lack of attention to customer account set up and failure to notify customer.
